## 9. Sprint Board Full Review & Lock

### Screen 4.1 — Sprint Board (Initiatives Populated)

Same Sprint Board layout from Screen 2.1 with capability cards now showing their initiative and refinement content.

Each capability card expanded to show:
- Initiative count and names (up to two lines before truncating with "show more")
- Milestone count where applicable
- Status: `Complete` (all required fields filled) or `Incomplete` (missing required fields)
- Incomplete indicator: a subtle flag on the card

